-- MOVES-Vontobel Financial Products Asia Pacific names Thomas Sussli as head
-- 
-- Thu Aug 07, 2014 12:20AM EDT
-- None



Aug 7 (Reuters) - Vontobel Financial Products (Asia Pacific) Pte Ltd named Thomas Sussli as its new head effective Oct. 1, and Eugen Lee as head of sales financial products, Asia Pacific, effective Sept. 1.

Sussli joins from Credit Suisse <CSGN.VX> and has extensive experience in the structuring, settlement and sale of structured products. Lee has earlier worked at JPMorgan Chase & Co <JPM.N>, HSBC and BBVA, where he was responsible for the Private Banks and Retail Investors client segments in Asia.  Both will be based in Singapore.